# 11. Receiver app flow

The actual application will get redirected to:

```text
https://actual-app/post-login?code=abc123
```

Then its backend should call:

```http
POST /auth/handoff/exchange
{
  "code": "abc123"
}
```

Arthur Core returns:

```json
{
  "userId": "testuser",
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "testuser@test.local",
  "roles": ["SELLER"],
  "appId": "B2BOOST_BE"
}
```

Then the actual app:

* creates its own local session
* sets its own cookie
* builds Spring Security context

